<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 15:14:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>乌克兰外长抵达中国讨论“公平和平”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-foreign-minister-arrives-china-discuss-fair-peace-2024-07-23/</link><description>乌克兰外长周二抵达中国，与外交部长王毅举行会谈，讨论如何在与俄罗斯的战争中实现“公平和平”，并讨论双边关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 14:27:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-foreign-minister-arrives-china-discuss-fair-peace-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国在兴奋剂纠纷中向美国挑战金牌炫耀权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-challenge-us-gold-medal-bragging-rights-amid-doping-rout-2024-07-23/</link><description>中国来到巴黎奥运会，期待着近几十年来亚洲体育强国屡见不鲜的金牌潮，但兴奋剂纠纷的阴影却笼罩着代表团。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 13:20:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-challenge-us-gold-medal-bragging-rights-amid-doping-rout-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>印度财政部长支持增加中国直接投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indias-finance-minister-backs-increasing-chinese-direct-investment-2024-07-23/</link><description>自2020年以来，新德里与北京关系日益紧张，导致资金流动受到干扰，印度财政部长支持其经济顾问的建议，允许更多中国投资进入该国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 12:20:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indias-finance-minister-backs-increasing-chinese-direct-investment-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国电动卡车初创公司 Windrose 将在美国 IPO 前筹集 2 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-electric-truck-startup-windrose-raise-200-mln-before-us-ipo-source-says-2024-07-23/</link><description>一位直接知情人士透露，中国电动卡车初创公司 Windrose 计划在最后一轮股权投资和债务融资中筹集 2 亿美元，然后再寻求在美国进行首次公开​​募股。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 11:17:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-electric-truck-startup-windrose-raise-200-mln-before-us-ipo-source-says-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>厄瓜多尔海军准备打击加拉帕戈斯群岛周围的非法捕鱼活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/ecuadors-navy-ready-combat-illegal-fishing-around-galapagos-islands-2024-07-23/</link><description>厄瓜多尔海军在与邻国盟友进行训练演习后，准备保护加拉帕戈斯群岛周围海域免受外国船只的非法捕鱼，这些船只每年都会到访，威胁该群岛水域的海洋野生动物。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 11:01:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/ecuadors-navy-ready-combat-illegal-fishing-around-galapagos-islands-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>通用汽车超出季度预期并上调预测，但股价跳水</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/gm-beats-second-quarter-expectations-raises-forecast-again-2024-07-23/</link><description>通用汽车周二公布的第二季度利润和收入超出了华尔街的预期，并在强劲的定价和汽油动力卡车需求的推动下，今年第二次上调了年度利润预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 10:31:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/gm-beats-second-quarter-expectations-raises-forecast-again-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：巨型股报告，哈里斯在框架内，中国摇摆不定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-07-23/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 10:17:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>五角大楼表达担忧后，克里姆林宫表示俄罗斯与中国的北极合作不针对任何人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-russian-arctic-cooperation-with-china-is-not-aimed-against-anyone-2024-07-23/</link><description>克里姆林宫周二表示，俄罗斯与中国在北极的合作并不针对任何其他国家，并表示美国对此类工作的批评是错误的。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 09:53:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-russian-arctic-cooperation-with-china-is-not-aimed-against-anyone-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>Forvia 和比亚迪将亚洲合作伙伴关系带到欧洲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/forvia-byd-bring-asian-partnership-europe-2024-07-23/</link><description>全球第七大汽车零部件供应商 Forvia 周二表示，将把与中国电池专家和汽车制造商比亚迪的合作伙伴关系带到欧洲。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 09:16:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/forvia-byd-bring-asian-partnership-europe-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>印度削减智能手机进口税以提振苹果</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-budget-india-cuts-import-tax-smartphones-boost-apple-2024-07-23/</link><description>印度宣布将手机和部分关键零部件的进口关税从20%下调至15%，此举将直接让苹果公司受益，尽管苹果公司在当地产量增加，但仍向印度进口高端智能手机。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 08:42:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-budget-india-cuts-import-tax-smartphones-boost-apple-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车在中国举步维艰。电动汽车能否帮助其在美国发展？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-is-reeling-china-can-evs-help-it-grow-us-2024-07-23/</link><description>这家全球第二大汽车制造商面临着令人烦恼的挑战，尤其是在中国。大众汽车规模较小的美国业务正在承担其最大的增长目标。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 07:19:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-is-reeling-china-can-evs-help-it-grow-us-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>台湾模拟中国导弹袭击，警报响起，街道空无一人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sirens-sound-streets-deserted-taiwan-simulates-chinese-missile-strike-2024-07-23/</link><description>周二，在台湾首都台北举行的模拟中国导弹袭击的年度空袭演习中，警报响起，道路空无一人，人们被命令呆在室内。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 06:44:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sirens-sound-streets-deserted-taiwan-simulates-chinese-missile-strike-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>日本最高发言人表示，日本将与美国合作促进台湾和平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan-will-work-with-us-taiwan-peace-top-spokesman-says-2024-07-23/</link><description>日本政府最高发言人在接受路透社独家采访时表示，无论谁在 11 月总统选举后入主白宫，日本都将继续与美国合作，促进台湾海峡的和平。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 06:39:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan-will-work-with-us-taiwan-peace-top-spokesman-says-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国降息未能重振铁矿石和铜矿</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-rate-cuts-fail-revive-iron-ore-copper-russell-2024-07-23/</link><description>中国11个月来首次下调主要短期和长期利率，引起了通常被认为是最大受益者的大宗商品的明显反应。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 05:51:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-rate-cuts-fail-revive-iron-ore-copper-russell-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>美国关税威胁迫在眉睫，数字税收谈判成为 G20 焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/digital-tax-talks-g20-spotlight-us-tariff-threat-looms-2024-07-23/</link><description>关于全球税收协议的谈判在 6 月 30 日截止日期之后仍在继续，各国政府目前正在等待本周举行的 20 国集团财长会议，以期在一项陷入僵局的大型跨国公司重新分配征税权的计划上取得进展。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 05:10:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/digital-tax-talks-g20-spotlight-us-tariff-threat-looms-2024-07-23/</guid></item></channel></rss>